H0.text: What is the equivalent Royal Navy rank to an Air Marshall in the R.A.F.. Rear Admiral

H1.text: What is the equivalent Royal Navy rank to an Air Marshall in the R.A.F.. Commodore

H2.text: What is the equivalent Royal Navy rank to an Air Marshall in the R.A.F.. Captain

H3.text: What is the equivalent Royal Navy rank to an Air Marshall in the R.A.F.. VAdm

A4.text: The rank is usually equivalent to a vice admiral or a lieutenant general.

A5.text: For example, the rank that later became air marshal would have been air vice-admiral.
